Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:52.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up in the morning, brushed my teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.14,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,In the blink of an eye, it's 10pm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.23,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we laughed a whole lot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.23,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a great time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:07.61,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, with my friends, acting like fools, being noisy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:10.70,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Fluttering, our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.37,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a coincidence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.87,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call this my first love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:20.04,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my character.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:26.09,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, will we be able to meet again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:29.17,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,As my eyelids close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:32.30,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you sparkling all over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:35.64,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was fun, too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:39.56,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:48.11,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,So happy, so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my pleasure to meet you, my new-found love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:54.37,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, we'll meet again tomorrow~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.53,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:24:01.58,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet immediately in our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:07.67,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,So have a good night
