Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Professor, nyan nyan~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinonome household was at peace again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Earth round?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do rockets fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do magnets pull toward each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this world can be proven by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are talks about the afterworld,{There are things that may be eliminated...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ghosts, ghost stories and other spiritual phenomena.{Spiritual phenomena such as a world after death, ghosts and ghost stories.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way those kinds of sleep-inducing things could be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad if they were...{Because... they must not be allowed to be.}{choose one - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in spiritualists!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my day off, I spent 8 hours going one-way to Mt. Osore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting closer to the summit, the beating of my heart increases{accelerates - kb_z}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a spiritualist really exists here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she would live alone here. {they?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have her summon something already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Please summon some soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubble, it's Soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mic test... mic test... mic test, test, test.{missing line - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sensation of helplessness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be there's someone called Soap...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's S-Soap.{timer got to be careful here cause she says some random b4 she says this...}{around 4:48.75 she's saying this sentance}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I keep asking... Eventually, a contradiction point will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the blood type of Soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try a simpler person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobunaga... Please summon Oda Nobunaga! {http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B9%94%E7%94%B0%E4%BF%A1%E9%95%B7}{lol im a fan of Oda Nobunaga too!}{Oda Nobunaga was just as bad as the rest of the late Sengoku period Daimyo and gets an unfair bad reputation}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejecting me before even trying to summon him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's old after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to look after her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't scold her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scolding people is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by knowing that, I should reap what I've sown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 5000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of men.{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong, Mai-chan! Didn't I just explain it?{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hit me if you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing. You've got incredible concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, it's even crueller than hitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I've just explained,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you lose, you defend. When you win, you hit. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now! Why did you hit me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I won just then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't now, was it? It was just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live for the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're that kind of living thing, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock, next comes paper. Rockscispaper doesn't count,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nano, nyan~{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's do it again. {let's start clear?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have zero motivation to play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of a clown can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming... mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hold on, Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan, w-what's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it had been reincarnated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will put this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, she looks really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, that doesn't matter. Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rockscispaper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... such a brutal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Mai-chan, that doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockscispaper doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, hitting with the Buddha doesn't count either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you can do it if you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why did you hit me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it properly just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it... Because I don't want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look at your Maitreya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going to the library to return the books!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you look after the house, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Nano's daruma has only one eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Professor gave it another eye, Professor might get praised!{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nano may say "it's okay to eat as many snacks as you like"!{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've got it a little bit wrong...{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nano's, so what do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might get mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get any snacks for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... here... and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakamoto, what should I do? This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it didn't have an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, try doing what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sakamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sakamoto-san, you're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late because it took me some time to choose some new books to borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what's with that stomach of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "Ehehe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.31,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is this some kind of game?{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano's little brother is about to be born!{kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play Kokkuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll briefly explain it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to prepare a piece of paper by drawing a gate in the middle like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you write "yes", "no" and the 50 characters of the Japanese syllabary on the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although in some regions, you're supposed to draw a fried tofu on the paper instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for Kokkuri-san to be able to come in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you open the north-facing window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you set this 10-yen coin on the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put both of our fingers on it and ask a question that you want to know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as a person's secret, or who someone likes, or something that's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, the 10-yen coin will move all by itself\N and Kokkuri-san will answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some taboos, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, don't do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, don't mess around when doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else you will be haunted by spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you stop halfway through, you will be haunted, so be wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty dangerous game, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why don't you give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow we have a mini-test, so everyone please study for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Postpone it, postpone it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't the outcome be exactly the same for you no matter how long it's postponed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Aioi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... about the test we had before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... That's a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about this thing that looks like it'd vanish\N pretty easily. Did you draw it, Sensei?{no idea some thing kiesou?}{As good as I can figure}{ニフラムで消えそうなキャラの絵を描いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I thought that if I included some\Npictures, the test might be a little easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You draw very interesting pictures, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad at drawing, so it was hard to understand wasn't it? {kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you include a picture that I've drawn next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw something really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My picture's going to be in the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said she'll put them in. {Sensei's going to put it in.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw something right now,\Nshe'll definitely put yours in, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "definitely", but it's still "maybe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... you're not going to draw something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One cool guy{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aioi-san, you're so good at drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not that good... I'm awesome at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, his name is Samidare George.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, what you'd call cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:23.95,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!{Also spoken at around this point, in a male voice}{either typeset or use default-alt - kb_z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naganohara-san, do you draw manga or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No{\fscx300}-{\r} Well, only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... Ah... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are much cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ripped off mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't rip it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you {\i1}did{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of rip-off is known as a homage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just admitted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything works for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses!{That reminds me of Houjou Souun from Sengoku Rance}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An intelligent and cool look that appeals to all women of any era!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is his eyesight bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should just wear contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're underneath his ears!{Referring to the glasses}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, this is a rip-off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk, tsk, tsk... they're sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From picking you up to serving you tea... you'll feel like a real lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the magic of Darjeeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't listen to my advice about contacts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, you don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, what's really cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, hold on... This... It's running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! It looks so fast and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rationally speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it rationally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew this while listening to jazz music.{also written on-screen}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sensei, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll hand out this morning's mini-test,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please pass them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep secret the fact that I draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I drew a picture like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, even though I lost control, only going to that level was a blessing amongst all the misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko's going to tease me for two or three days though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep my chin up and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-sensei, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm onomatopoeia!{start it after the gibberish}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:20.43,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but say "Cock-a-doodle-do" in Japanese even though it's not Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:23.49,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The next Nichijou is the sixth. Look forward to it.
